title: Green Hutts Natural Juice Bar and Vegan Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Ghanian
description: Vegan place serving natural fruit juices, pastries, and food. A retail area sells an array of red, gold and green products, Rasta wear, African beads, oils, incense, and herbal food products. Open during the daytime, and on Saturday til 10pm.
